and can readily use.

\item[Pulse].   A   five-second    increment    of    game
time  A,hich  regulates  actions   while   on   the
Tactical Display.

\item[Ranged  Zone].  The   hexes   radiating   out   from
a figure's  front  hexes  into  which  that  figure
can see and fire a weapon, spell, etc.


\item[Sheltered   Hex].   Any   hex   containing   physic-
