\subsubsection{Damage affecting Fatigue is absorbed by armor.}

     Each type of     armor      has      a      Protection
Rating,     w@@ich     indicates     the     amount      of
damage points subtracted       from       every       suc-
cessful        attack.      When      a       figure's       Fatigue
reaches        0,      any      further       damage       affecting
Fatigue is          subtracted      from      EnduraRce.       n-
stead.   However,   a   figure   cannot   lose    1-ati@@@@e
and  Endurance  as   a   result   of   a   single   StriKe
Check.
